Interface Rentable<T extends Vehicle>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of vehicle that can be rented, extending the Vehicle class
All Known Implementing Classes:
Minivan, Sedan, SUV, Truck, Vehicle
public interface Rentable<T extends Vehicle>
Rentable interface for defining the rental properties of a vehicle. This interface specifies the method for obtaining the daily rental rate of a vehicle.
Version:
1.0
Author:
DT and Aakriti

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    double getDailyRate()
    Registers the daily rental rate for the vehicle.

  • Method Details

    • getDailyRate

      double getDailyRate()
      Registers the daily rental rate for the vehicle. The rate is used to calculate the total rental cost based on the number of rental days.
      Returns:
      the daily rental rate as a double
